<td valign="MIDDLE"><font face="Verdana" size="2" color="000000">hello. lvl 4 ench here. heh will i will not begin to act like i know anything about ench beause i dont and thats why i am here. i am posting this so i might have a couple questions cleared if i may. <br>
Races: i have read most of these messages and haven't heard much about best races. i have made erudite. base int 142, base charisma 95. thought this wouldn't be too bad with stein of mog and a crude stein. any thoughts?<br>
Good or bad?: i have read a lot about pets being very good/very bad. same with dmg spells and solo vs. grouping. cant anyone make up mind?<br>
   i have been playing eq a while and though i have no high lvl's &lt;highest 25 druid&gt; i am a very smart person and have heard ench are very fun race to play. i hope to play them to fullest and would like all the help i may get. in EQ or e-mail.<br>
thanks.<p>

